pop-before-smtp-init-1.25-Orig - as-shipped original 1.25 init script
pop-before-smtp.init - result of applying pop-before-smtp-1.25-syslog.patch to init script

Contributed by Stig Hackvan. Note that this patch also incidentally
switches the tail option to File::Tail so pop-before-smtp won't
re-read the maillog on startup.
